casebody.data:
Donald R. HOLBROOK, Superintendent, Washington State Penitentiary, petitioner,
v.
Dwayne Anthony WOODS. No. 14-931. Supreme Court of the United States May 18, 2015.

Opinion

Motion of respondent for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Ninth Circuit denied.
